<br>
Think about it.  Mediate increases the amount of mana you gain back per 'tick'.  So due to the way this works some levels 4% more meditate skill will not actually increase the amount of mana you med back per tick.  Other levels it -might- add 1 mana per tick.  Thus it's possible that in a best case scenerio you'll gain an additional 10 mana per _minute_.  So with that information, look at the spells you normally cast and how much mana they take, and you can see that it's likely that a +% meditate item is fairly useless.<br>
<br>
Now the test that I did was a long time ago, and maybe they changed something, but I doubt it.  I personnally think that anyone saying that they med faster with a + meditate item is probably effected by the placebo effect.  If someone actually tests this out I'd love to see the data...<br>
